<h2>RackMonkey Report</h2>
<p>This is an early version of the report section, which will provide statistics on the items stored in RackMonkey.</p>

<h3>Summary</h3>
<ul>
	<li>There are <TMPL_VAR NAME=rack_count> <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME=base_url>?view=rack">racks</a> with a total size of <TMPL_VAR NAME=total_rack_space> U</li>
	<li>There are <TMPL_VAR NAME=device_count> <a href="<TMPL_VAR NAME=base_url>?view=device">devices</a> using a total of <TMPL_VAR NAME=used_rack_space> U</li>
	<li>There is <TMPL_VAR NAME=free_rack_space> U of free space in the racks</li>
</ul>

<h3>Customers</h3>
